727238f-a.title: Queens: Lincoln Street - Van Wyck Boulevard
727238f-a.text:
Lincoln Street, south side, east of Van Wyck Boulevard, showing
the Greenwood house, which has been in the Van Sicklen family from some
date prior to 1859.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
